Class LEAP_POINT_MAPPING

java.lang.Object
com.sun.jna.Structure
komposten.leapjna.leapc.data.LEAP_POINT_MAPPING
@Deprecated @FieldOrder({"frame_id","timestamp","nPoints","pPoints","pIDs"}) public class LEAP_POINT_MAPPING extends Structure
Deprecated.

A notification that a device's point mapping has changed.

It contains the entire set of points being mapped.

Since:
LeapJna 1.0.0, Ultraleap Orion SDK 4.0.0
